plan.name: plan
plan.code:
<dl class="plan"
    data-plan-id="{@id}"
    data-view-href="{@permalink}"
    data-edit-href="{@id,get_edit_post_link}"
    style="color: {@driver.colour,contrast_color}; background-color: {@driver.colour};">
    <dt class="name">Job</dt>
    <dd class="name">{@post_title}</dd>
    <dt class="driver">Driver</dt>
    <dd class="driver">{@driver}</dd>
    <dt class="date">Date</dt>
    <dd class="date">{@plan_date,fmt_date}</dd>
    <dt class="pu_loc">Location</dt>
    <dd class="pu_loc" title="{@pu_loc,esc_attr}">{@pu_loc}</dd>
    <dt class="pu_time">Time</dt>
    <dd class="pu_time">{@pu_time}</dd>
    <dt class="flight">Flight</dt>
    <dd class="flight">{@flight}</dd>
    <dt class="vehicle">Vehicle</dt>
    <dd class="vehicle">{@vehicle}</dd>
    <dt class="contact">Contact Name</dt>
    <dd class="contact">{@contact_name}</dd>
    <dt class="contact">Contact Phone</dt>
    <dd class="contact">{@contact_phone}</dd>
</dl>
